cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with cross-lingual transfer learning and NLP tasks. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training a multilingual neural network. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with transfer learning and generalization across tasks and languages. It may also fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as transfer learning and generalization are important topics in this field. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves training a neural network for transfer learning.
